snippet.title: Longplay of Uchuu Keiji Tamashii: The Space Sheriff Spirits
snippet.description:
Longplay of Uchuu Keiji Tamashii: The Space Sheriff Spirits, played as the NTSC-J version on the PlayStation 2. This game's version was released on May 25th, 2006. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!
